graph TD
    A[Start: Phishing Alert Received] --> B{Did User Click Link?}
    B -- Yes --> C[Isolate Workstation]
    B -- No --> D{Is there an Attachment?}
    
    C --> E[Reset User Credentials]
    E --> F[Check for Lateral Movement]
    
